He condemned white supremacists and Antifa equally, which was appropriate, as they both suck and Trump was right to say so.
You can ask his black supporters – starting with our boss, Kanye West and Ben Carson – what happens to them as a result of their support for Trump. They get attacked plenty for it, but not by Trump. They get attacked by the left.
I realize there are many things Trump has said and done that the left insist are “racist dog whistles” or whatever, but show me a statement he’s made, or an action he’s taken, that represents evidence of actual hate toward anyone.
