I don’t think you can. Yet we know Ilhan Omar hates Jews, and she’s learning nothing except how not to embarrass her Democrat colleagues by being so obvious about it.
Nice try taking the focus off of you, but we’re going to make sure it gets put right back on you, Congresswoman. You are a disgrace. You’re worse than Steve King, and the Republicans stripped him of all his committee assignments.
I await Nancy Pelosi’s decision to do the same to Omar, and I’d like to know why it hasn’t already happened.
